text:
Wonderful experience! Love the car, was treated wonderfully. I did have an issue with the financing but the owner went above and beyond to make sure I was taken care of. I was very surprised and am more than satisfied with the result. I would definitely recommend Tameron Hyundai if you are looking for a car and want to be treated with respect.

Update 8 months later;
Still happy with the car and when I take it in for oil changes it is always a pleasant experience
